tip.text: The cognac flavour is awesome! Just a hint of bitterness yet rich and smooth.
Cocktails are excellent! Creative concoctions that are both fun and delicious. Really cosy and quaint space. Will definitely come back for the food next time!
The BLT Croissant Plate is amazing. Succulent strips of bacon wrapped in layers of flaky croissant. Definitely coming back for more. Awesome service too!
Great restaurant. Appetiser, love the foie gras spring roll. Desserts are amazing. Chocolate fondant and mystere maison is good. It's really a pleasant surprise!
Love the chicken rice and red bean soup. Really is the most beautiful restaurant in Hoi An. Decent food and a meal under USD10.
